title: Caliber Press - Baker Street (1989 Series)
description: Great series with a London/Punk female Sherlock Holmes. Thanks go to the original scanners (unknown). I did scan issue #5 and #9 as it was missing from a previous torrent. I still have to scan the missing issues but at least the first storyline is complete (I have the original series just not easy access to a scanner) Hopefully I'll finish scanning all missing issues by the end of summer.
